headline: Week’s Best: Get In on Gold and Silver?
summary: Precious metals have been on a tear lately.  For this week’s Barron’s Advisor Big Q, we asked wealth management professionals whether it is too late for investors to get in on these rallies.  Financial planning is far more complex today than in years past, partly because people are living longer and because there are many more investment opportunities available.
